WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:06.000
The quickest way to search the Werkstatt is with the simple search in the upper right-hand corner.

00:06.000 --> 00:11.000
You can search formulae collections, charter corpora and E-Lexicon articles.

00:11.000 --> 00:14.000
Lemma search and advanced search are also possible.

00:14.000 --> 00:18.000
These will be covered in their own videos.

00:18.000 --> 00:22.000
To search for a term, go the the simple search field,

00:22.000 --> 00:24.000
type in the desired term,

00:24.000 --> 00:27.500
suggestions for phrases to search are shown

00:27.500 --> 00:31.000
(you need not choose any of these),

00:31.000 --> 00:35.000
then click on the box(es)

00:35.000 --> 00:37.000
for the corpora you wish to search,

00:37.000 --> 00:38.500
Formulae and Charters in this case,

00:38.500 --> 00:41.000
and then hit "Enter".

00:41.000 --> 00:45.000
The Werkstatt will be searched and the results shown here.

00:45.000 --> 00:49.000
You can filter, sort and download the results.

00:49.000 --> 00:52.000
These functions will be explained in their own vidoes.

